This folder contains the crank power window controller firmware source code and PCB design.

This controller replaces the crank window mechanism and is intended to be applied in retro cars where the owner
doesn't want to install the buttons when installing the power window drive.

The main features are:
- soft motor start and stop.
- full opening or closing mode without holding the lever.
- an input from the car alarm or central lock system for closing the windows.
- protection from motor overload or short circuit with a current sensor.
- protection from output short circuit to the ground or battery.


